[Black "Chapter 12 Push Variation"]

{The "Maroczy Bind" is set up against 3...d3. White's move order matters: prophylactic h3 preventing ...Bg4/Ng4, and Nc3 after ...Nf6, avoiding ...Bxc3.}

1. e4 c5 2. d4 cxd4 3. c3 d3 {[%entry]} 4. Bxd3 d6 5. c4 Nc6 6. h3 g6 7. Nf3 Bg7 8. O-O Nf6 9. Nc3 O-O 10. Be3 Nd7 11. Rc1 Nc5 12. Bb1 *
